      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn15.11:1.1",
          "pli": "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. ",
          "en": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn15.11:1.2",
          "pli": "Tatra kho … pe … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn15.11:1.3",
          "pli": "“Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro. ",
          "en": "“Mendicants, transmigration has no known beginning. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn15.11:1.4",
          "pli": "Pubbā koṭi na paññāyati avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ sandhāvataṃ saṃsarataṃ. ",
          "en": "No first point is found of sentient beings roaming and transmigrating, hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn15.11:1.5",
          "pli": "Yaṃ, bhikkhave, passeyyātha duggataṃ durūpetaṃ niṭṭhamettha gantabbaṃ: ",
          "en": "When you see someone in a sorry state, in distress, you should conclude: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn15.11:1.6",
          "pli": "‘amhehipi evarūpaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ iminā dīghena addhunā’ti. ",
          "en": "‘In all this long time, we too have undergone the same thing.’ "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn15.11:1.7",
          "pli": "Taṃ kissa hetu … pe … ",
          "en": "Why is that? Transmigration has no known beginning. … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn15.11:1.8",
          "pli": "yāvañcidaṃ, bhikkhave, alameva sabbasaṅkhāresu nibbindituṃ alaṃ virajjituṃ alaṃ vimuccitun”ti. ",
          "en": "This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and freed regarding all conditions.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn15.11:1.9",
          "pli": "Paṭhamaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
